# ROBOVANTA Hackathon - Dataset Download Walkthrough

## Summary

Successfully built a **complete local dataset repository** (~3 GB, 278 files) for the ROBOVANTA Hackathon problem:
*AI-Driven Automated Crop Type Classification, Moisture Stress Detection & Irrigation Advisory using Optical & Microwave Satellite Data.*

**AOI**: North Karnataka Agricultural Belt, India (74.5°E–76.0°E, 15.0°N–16.5°N)  
**CRS**: EPSG:4326 (WGS84)  
**Period**: 2023–2024  

---

